subject: Loose cable on brake pedal
description_text: So I ordered the pro x ultra and got it today and there is this loose cable that is not plugged into anything. Where does it go?

conversations.body_text: Hi Brayden Divine, If you did not purchase the base plate, you can simply ignore this cable, as it is used for the LED light strip on the base plate.

Ok, thank you.
